{"tha-ap384:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap384:0.2":"Avataphalavagga ","tha-ap384:0.3":"Labujadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap384:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap384:1.2":"asim aramiko tada; ","tha-ap384:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap384:1.4":"gacchantam anilanjase. ","tha-ap384:2.1":"Labujassa phalam gayha, ","tha-ap384:2.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap384:2.3":"Akase thitako santo, ","tha-ap384:2.4":"patiganhi mahayaso. ","tha-ap384:3.1":"Vittisanjananam mayham, ","tha-ap384:3.2":"ditthadhammasukhavaham; ","tha-ap384:3.3":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap384:3.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap384:4.1":"Adhigacchim tada pitim, ","tha-ap384:4.2":"vipulanca sukhuttamam; ","tha-ap384:4.3":"Uppajjateva ratanam, ","tha-ap384:4.4":"nibbattassa tahim tahim. ","tha-ap384:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap384:5.2":"yam phalamadadim tada; ","tha-ap384:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap384:5.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap384:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap384:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap384:6.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap384:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap384:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap384:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap384:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap384:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap384:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap384:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma labujadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap384:10.1":"Labujadayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}